wed by the\nsubsequent process of parton showering that turns the jets into hadrons, in\nhigh energy $pp$ and $p\\bar p$ collisions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 May 2015 13:00:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
